# VHS demo tape — regenerate demo.gif with:  vhs demo.tape
# https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs

Output demo.gif
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1100
Set Height 640
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 18

Type "memsync init"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "# a memory written in Claude now shows up in Codex — encrypted across machines"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "memsync status"
Enter
Sleep 3s
